<i>noun</i>: 피멍 [피멍], 타박상 [타ː박쌍], 멍 [멍] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>피멍 [피멍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bruise; contusion</dd><br>
<dd>피부 속에 핏줄이 터져서 피가 엉긴 덩이.</dd><br>
<dd>Blood clots from a burst blood vessel under the skin.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deep scars</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 씻기지 않을 만큼 분하거나 억울한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A very angry and sad incident that one cannot get over.</dd><br>
<dt>타박상 [타ː박쌍]</dt><br>
<dd>bruise; contusion</dd><br>
<dd>단단한 물건에 맞거나 부딪쳐서 생긴 상처.</dd><br>
<dd>A wound made by being hit by or clashed against something hard.</dd><br>
<dt>멍 [멍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bruise; black and blue</dd><br>
<dd>부딪히거나 맞아서 피부 바로 아래에 퍼렇게 피가 맺힌 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the flesh right beneath the skin becomes discolored, taking on a bluish hue due to being bruised by a blow or collision.</dd><br>
<dd>2. scar; damage; shock</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어떤 일로 인해 생긴 마음의 상처나 충격.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A psychological wound or shock caused by a certain event.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>